General Description

Enumerations

enum  en_trig_input_pdma0_tr_t
 For PERI_ver2: the enumerated type that represents a trigger multiplexer group #0 input signals, used by Cy_TrigMux_Connect and Cy_TrigMux_SwTrigger functions. Refer to a family-specific device header file, e.g. <PDL_DIR>/devices/include/psoc6_02_config.h.
